                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d83">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-11-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 29, 1893</hi>
                        </date>. (Received November 29.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Thompson reports that the attack of the insurgents on Nictheroy and Santa
                    Catharina has been repulsed, the <hi rend="italic">Pallas</hi> being wrecked and
                    the <hi rend="italic">Madeira</hi> burned. He says that the situation appears
                    favorable to the Government.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
